<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<section class="policy-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="policy-chip">Educational Tourism</span>
    <h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>
    <p>
      These terms explain our booking rules, minimum seat policy, payment flow,
      cancellation process.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="container policy-page my-5">
  <div class="policy-card">
    <h3>1. Booking Requests</h3>
    <p>
      All tour bookings are treated as requests first. A booking is not confirmed
      until it is approved by admin and payment is completed by the user.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-card">
    <h3>2. Minimum Seats Policy</h3>
    <p>
      Every educational tour may have a minimum student requirement. If minimum
      seats are not completed, the booking may remain in low booking status.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Admin can wait for more students</li>
      <li>Admin can reschedule the batch</li>
      <li>Admin can cancel/refund the booking</li>
      <li>Admin can proceed with special approval</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-card">
    <h3>3. Payment Rules</h3>
    <p>
      Payment is allowed only after admin approval. After successful payment, the
      booking status will be marked as confirmed.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-card">
    <h3>4. Cancellation & Refund</h3>
    <p>
      Users may cancel pending or approved bookings before final confirmation.
      Refund decisions depend on booking status, admin policy, and tour conditions.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-card">
    <h3>6. User Responsibility</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Users must provide correct college, coordinator, and contact details</li>
      <li>Users must select correct batch and student count</li>
      <li>Misuse of the platform may result in request rejection</li>
      <li>Users must read Privacy Policy before submitting requests</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-card">
    <h3>7. Admin Rights</h3>
    <p>
      Admin has the right to approve, reject, reschedule, or cancel booking and
       minimum seats, payment status,
      and operational feasibility.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-card">
    <h3>8. Contact</h3>
    <p>
      For terms-related questions, contact us at
      <a href="mailto:rk8313681@gmail.com">rk8313681@gmail.com</a>
      or call
      <a href="tel:+919695959664">+91 9695959664</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>